Property.Description: This indicates whethere the account has been terminated or not (Y/N)
Property.Name: Terminated

Property.Name: Deleted

Property.Description: Username or login that needs to be created. Required for creation.
Property.Name: UserName

Property.Description: Namespace uniquely identifying that username or login. Required for creation
Property.Name: Name_Space

Property.Description: Uniquely generated account ID. This property gets set by the pipeline.
Property.Name: _AccountID

Property.Description: Flag indicates whether DSP should be applied to a newly created account. T for True or 1 and F for False or 0. Required for creation.
Property.Name: ApplyDefaultSecurityPolicy

Property.Description: This flag indicates whether account ancestor's account template should be applied to an account.
Property.Name: ApplyAccountTemplate

Property.Description: Indicates whether old subscriptions will be truncated on move account action. This property is only considered on account updates when account ancestor changed (Account Move). This property is only considered when ApplyAccountTemplate property is set to true.
Property.Name: TruncateOldSubscriptions

Property.Description: Transaction cookie value used for processes to enlist in DTC transaction. Should have empty value when metered. The value gets set once the pipeline retrieves it from each machine. The cookie is machine specific and is unique to a machine.
Property.Name: TransactionCookie

Property.Description: Default pricelist assigned to account.
Property.Name: Pricelist

Property.Description: Currency assigned to account. Required while creating account.
Property.Name: Currency

Property.Description: Language associated with the account. Required while creation.
Property.Name: Language

Property.Description: Usage cycle type associated with the account (daily, weekly, biweeky, semi-monthly, monthly, quarterly, annually.) On-demand is no longer supported.
Property.Name: UsageCycleType

Property.Description: Day of month that the user wants to get billed on.
Property.Name: DayOfMonth

Property.Description: Tax exempt indicator: T for Yes or success or true or 1 and F for no or failure or false or 0.
Property.Name: TaxExempt

Property.Description: Tax Exempt ID, if applicable.
Property.Name: TaxExemptID

Property.Description: This field indicates whether the statement will be delivered via Paper copy/e-mail/emailLink/both/none
Property.Name: SPrintDelivery

Property.Description: This field indicates whether the Invoice will be delivered via Paper copy/e-mail/emailLink/both/none
Property.Name: IPrintDelivery

Property.Description: This field indicates the language to be used for the Invoice, values could be English/German/French
Property.Name: InvoiceLanguage

Property.Description: This field indicates the format to be used for the Invoice, values could be None/Legal/Standard
Property.Name: InvoiceFormat

Property.Description: This field indicates the Summary for the current charges is needed on the invoice or not. values could be (Y/N)
Property.Name: CurrChargeSummary

Property.Description: Marks the invoice PDF to be be put in the SpecialInvoiceRun folder. These invoices are reviewed manually for key customers.
Property.Name: SpecialInvoiceRun

Property.Description: Indicates that the account should not receive dunning notifications during statement runs.
Property.Name: DunningExempt
